The need for speed The Run competes across America. 
Review 
Originally a race without problem is because of a series of stupid mistakes of people who have nothing to do with a routine early morning shift at work. 
It fills up to a certain extent the ambition of each, but it is pointless if nobody wants to do something more. 
The new party subtitled The Run has produced great expectations before his exit. 
He promised to take a new direction with a series of race Need for Speed and out a kind of game from the jouables parties that would not only with points. 
We were therefore curious how will be added to the passages in which the main hero comes out of his car and does what he wants. 
As is already in the NFS series, the result is completely different than atttendait. 
These are potentially racing games arcades, but the whole shoot down because of some unnecessary mistakes that have existed for several years. 
These are not really mistakes, but rather the expression of an incomprehensible laziness on the part of developers. 
The adventure begins very well. 
You are caught in the adventure whose main hero Jack has characters and to resolve to participate in illegal races across America. 
You sit behind the wheel on the West Coast in San Francisco and your mission is the first in New York. 
The idea has some interesting elements. 
The route is divided into ten stages and then in more than 50 races. 
The result is that each race is on a different route and stages in different environments that differ quite well and are interesting. 
The player did not feel one moment that the game is proposing something similar. 
Some environments are quite nice, even if the technical level graphic is of the same type as the previous series. 
Finally, this is not the end of the world. 
But driving through the desert, in autumn landscapes or in highly snow-covered mountains is very pleasant. 
The tests are an atypical element. 
For example in the desert you find yourself in a sand storm that you diminish significantly visibility. 
Then in the mountains you must be careful to ensure that an avalanche you do not fall over. 
The different races are structured behind the other. 
There was only a small number, but it is enough. 
There are moments you surpass the required number of opponents (as in a classic race) and then you will be running against the clock (classic duel with the clock) and then you yet another duel with an opponent. 
From time to time you have the police who enters the game and who is trying to make the situation difficult. 
The novelty is the crossings outside the vehicle. 
It is rather una interactive animation when most of the time Jack escaped before someone and you have to help by banging on the right button at the right time. 
Nothing complicated. 
What is surprising is that there are fewer moments of this kind than what you expect (to be practical there are only three). 
The result is that because this is not likely to hinder and, in the context described above, in the elements that enhances the game. 
The model is in the tradition of previous games. 
This means that currently there is nothing extraordinary, but we cannot say that this is negative. 
With regard to the realistic simulation you have to look elsewhere. 
But although you can find better in the conccurrence the pattern of conduct goes very well with the type of design of the races. 
So everything is OK. 
The problems begin to appear after some time. 
The diffférence model is not yet at the point. 
We do not expect this game complicated deformation and collisions, but when you do not have, in a collision with any object, the slightest idea of how is your car, this is not completely right. 
During the tight exceedances sometimes you touch each other slightly but otherwise your car in mad acrobatics. 
Or crumbs. 
Thanks to the system of recovery that is not really a problem, but it really upsets. 
The recovery is so that when you have broken or you are left in the stage the game takes you back at the time of the last point on the route. 
But you have only five redémarrages. 
When you used the 5 redémarrages you have to start the game from the start. 
It is a tool, if something is not happening as it is, that old adage on which you can really count. 
Sometimes the redémarrages do not help, and we need to find a solution in remémorrant memory piece of route. 
The big problem of this game is that the same actions are in the same places. 
For example, there are subtle shifts that we need to move from a certain way otherwise it does not. 
Otherwise you have on a given place "civilian" vehicles still in the same configuration as you first, fifth, 5 seconds ahead or one minute late. 
Angry situations when you see easily move your opponent between two cars oncoming and when you arrive, you, you must be set aside and conturner or halt. 
If you go out to him because it is "calculated" in such a way that the situation is still very close to your nose. 
Opponents still have other advantages. 
During the time of the game, you, you arrive in some places, again without worrying about time, and you always have the same adversary that precedes the same place. 
This irritates the end of the game when you drive on a long bridge in the opposite direction. 
The opponent must go before you. 
When he goes before you hide the sight of the other vehicles in the opposite direction and you get a good number of times. 
One can understand that the purpose of this game is to do something exciting and full of adrédaline, but it is clear that you are bored quickly. 
And it is a pity, because through a simple model of the game is interesting and places with so much that you do not have the time to follow everything that happens. 
And that is equal if it is because of the concept of 50 unique itineraries, that the order of the races is such that there is no chance of being bored or something else. 
The original idea is the change of car racing. 
You must be careful with gasoline pumps on the routes because you can change cars, though most of the time you enough. 
Cars are divided into three categories. 
Sports cars are ideal for cities, gas-guzzlers for straight highways and super sports cars in exotic garb on the highly technical lines on the winding roads in the mountains. 
And the challenges, which are races in particular places that you know of adventure, goes very well with the main regime in history. 
You get not only medals but also experience that add to your profile that is common to the challenges and adventure. 
When you have reached the highest level of driver, different objects are starting to be unlocked: 
It goes online with the Autolog function that compares your results with those of other players and you have other functions in the community. 
One of the most difficult shots to understand is the situation of the last race of the adventure. 
You arrive with your car in the subway tunnel (sounds like) where you drive in the dark on the tracks (it is). 
Your speedometer is between 150 and 200 kilometers per hour (a priori) and behind you is a subway train that sends you the car directly to the scrap metal. 
In the preparation we had a discussion for a few days to know if someone has really looked at the creation of this game or whether the authors we really take for fools. 
The technical part of the game is not dead, but the visual part is generally pleasant and in some cases really super. 
What is annoying is that in more extreme situations, imaging is not the level and in some cases tragically. 
This is especially accidents with a large number of participants when a fluid imagery is nothing. 
The noise is good and the runway is the choice. 
In order to please the greatest number and particularly to the young audience a new soundtrack was created in the style "I blend," but we can expect that no one will buy the game for music. 
General impression of Need for Speed: the Run is really confused. 
If the game didn't have these stupid mistakes we could say without fear that this is the best production of NFS in recent years. 
But this game gives the impression of not being finished. 
The amusement is really well but prepare you for the mistakes you pat in the eye with the force of an aerodrome reflector. 
The Velvet Students in concert with the chorus of Charles University 
The festival Festa Academica proposed for the third time the festivities linking the International Day student with the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution with a musical party. 
During the festival occur 20 choirs of graduate schools and secondary classes. 
The highlight of the festival consists of two orgnisés concerts on 17 November. 
"Charles University has an important part in this festival." 
"One of the choirs there is the Choir of the Faculty of Pedagogy and Humanities, the festival committee seat President Vaclav Hampl," said the head of the organizing team Jakub Calou. 
The highlight of the festival is the concert by the Choir of colleges and secondary classes held with free entry on November 17 from 14 hours in space before the National Library technical Dejvice. 
There is the composition of the well-known Czech musician Karel Ruzicka, Jazz Celebration mass. 
In the evening the concert "velvet students" in the premises of the National House in Vinohrady during which occur choruses of graduate schools, as well as that of Charles University. 
Academica Festa is intended not only to celebrate with dignity the International Day of students and remember the 22nd anniversary of the Velvet Revolution, but also to present to the public a choir music of the highest level and develop the creative cooperation of young people. 
The main organizer is the EU researchers from the Czech Republic in cooperation with the school Jan Kepler. 
All the action is placed under the aegis of Bohuslav Svoboda, Mayor of Prague and Vaclav Hampl, Rector of Charles University. 
The festival takes place from 16 to 20 November in Prague and Pardubice. 
The program also offers high-level concerts, msicales meetings, a student happening and other activities. 
Interested parties will find all the information on the Internet pages of the festival, festaacademica CS. 
Vicenova, Ambassador EU: 
The Czechs are behaving like négativistes and Eurosceptics 
"The Treaty of Lisbon has radically removed the balance between the institutions." 
"I do not expect a harsh war." 
"It will be 5.6 years before the situation is calm and that all players get used to their new role," as Vicenova Miléna began his presentation at the Faculty of Law the Czech ambassador near the European Union. 
When she was able to describe the various bodies of the EU and their relations so understandable and visible, to the point that a large number of speakers from the Faculty of Law of Charles University might envy, she has shown how it takes its motto "understandable and openly about Europe" very seriously. 
Ms. Vicenova has paid tribute to the work of Herman Van Rompuye, the new permanent President of the European Council. 
"From the outset echoed the criticism that it is bland, that it is a rond-de-cuir, that he cannot rempplir any mission and I have to say that he has cut the breath to everyone because he holds his role to perfection." 
"It is a man who knows how to listen to 27 member states, communicate with them and has a clear vision of the direction of Europe." 
She explained the new post of High Representative for foreign affairs and defence policy within the framework of an answer to the question: "Who is the European Union?" to which telephone number should I call? ," so as an important step towards unity and greater transparency of the policy of the EU states, such as China or India. 
Nobody wants to ban our syrecky (cheese cooked very strong) 
Ms. Vicenova also lived, live and will live in a time near the European Council. 
She called the Czech presidency two years of success. 
The Czech have resolved the crisis, the gas crisis or organized a summit for an Eastern Partnership. 
She described the collapse of the government very negative and has damaged the image of the Czech Republic. 
The Czech representation in the EU is currently very busy. 
In the words of Ambassador, "beat" not only for the presidency, but also for the financial crisis that continues to be resolved even now. 
We must approve the new septimal budget of the Union, which becomes very complicated because of the current economic situation. 
As it would appear that the budget will be thin and economies, what branch will be the priority, which countries will be helped the least, everything has to be resolved within the framework of future negotiations. 
Ambassador recalled its slogans with which it arrived in Brussels "for a Europe understandable." 
"I definitely don't like abbreviations, foreign words, jargon that nobody understands. 
As must understand the citizen that it is true that in Brussels nobody gherkins rings or twisted, differemment large bananas or that nobody has banned syrecky." 
It wants to better use the environment of the EU and see more Czechs in the European institutions. 
A multi-speed Europe ahead 
According to the ambassador the Czechs have a reputation for being Eurosceptics and people who do not see things in their negative aspect more than positively. 
It is sorry to see a small Czech representation in European institutions. 
The fault is the result of several factors, such as the timidity of our candidates, their inability to write a letter of motivation and low support from the Czech side. 
In addition to a Czech presidency success then underlined the strength and cooperation of the Visegrad Group. 
"Believe me, when they come to me the Poles, the Magyar, Slovak, French told me: ' Hey, what do you do there, what is still the Visegrad?" and it is not at all happy. " 
According to Ms. Vicenova, in the near future there are new tough rules on fiscal policy facing the member countries. 
This is the concept of a two-speed Europe, if not a multi-speed, which prevails rather than a "new European Federation." 
"We have countries in the euro area and others outside the zone." 
"We have the Schengen area, we have also the institute for enhanced cooperation." 
First it was said that cooperation among the countries who want and those who do not wish to remain in their corner." 
"There will be a lot of institutes of this kind and there will be a Europe really at two speeds," expects Mrs. Vicenova. 
From this point of view it has also appreciated the mission of the Czech Republic and Herman Van Rompuye to determine the basis on which all the themes that have an impact on the EU must be debated between all members of the EU and not just the memebres of the eurozone. 
Story of a mark: 
The innovative IBM begins the second century of its existence 
If someone had to look for the word that expresses the IBM strategy, the closest would be "the long term." 
For a wide audience IBM is the symbol of the technological revolution, is a firm considered very current and yet since its inception it has passed 100 years. 
The basis of this long-term strategy has been thrown by the first head of the firm, the visionary Thomas J. Watson Sr. 
He has left this slogan that a large number of global problems can be solved if people are willing to consider. 
Its slogan "PENSE'!" has become the footprint around which will develop the life of a future giant (and also the title of the internal magazine that IBM began publishing in 1935). 
It was the basis of the culture of the company soignement developed by Watson. 
IBM means a long-term thinking of continuing movements directed towards the future. 
IBM has survived 100 years thanks to the fact that it still remained true to its core values and has not been afraid to change all the others around it. 
This allowed us during our first century to transform the technology, business and society. 
We hope that in the second century we will achieve even more " délaré for the anniversary of the current director of the firm Samuel J. Palmisano. 
A well-prepared system 
Watson, in the 1930s, began to deal with its employees as Bata Czech Republic - people from IBM were the only one of the first American to have paid vacations, employer-paid more uniform elegant employee and a well developed system of rewards for inventors and commmerciaux. 
IBM has a system of relationships with the client well developed. 
The company was initially inspired by the discovery of talent - as one of the first companies to have abolished all forms of discrimination and thus could have the choice. 
The current plan is completely in the spirit of the anti-discrimination strategy because it will be a woman - Virginia Rometty - who should replace Palmisano at the head of IBM. 
IBM has been working for 30 years and currently holds the position of Head of Sales, Marketing and Strategy. 
IBM in recent years is the so-called jamy, brain - online discussion from many future strategies and innovations. 
It is not surprising that he has a lot of ideas - in the firm nearly 500,000 people who work. 
An institution with a good name 
It is the internal and external image of the company to ensure a secure position in the business areas. 
"Since the beginning IBM had a concept of institution rather than a technology firm," said Rosabeth Moss Kanter, Professor of Economics at the School of Economics at Harvard and author of the book on IBM. 
"IBM is not a technlogique firm, but a firm that helps to solve problems in the world of business by using its technology," added Geogre Colony of the consulting firm Forrester Research. 
As the firm itself there is a difference between entering the market and create this market. 
IBM - or the "Big Blue," as it is called colloquially in the United States with regard to its slogan - in a hundred years it has grown to become one of the largest global firms. 
This is obviously the most versatile technology firm - it develops software, hardwares, infrastructure, housing, services at the level of server products to nanotechnology. 
It has many patents of all American technology firms and five of its employees received a Nobel Prize. 
Among his discoveries such as the distributor of banknotes, the payment card, the financial swap, the code bar or the disk. 
IBM rose this year with $220 billion in the second largest technology firm by market capitalization (the first is Apple), when for the first time in 1996 it was Microsoft. 
Overview in advance 
