This was the work of the Cali who identified the corpse of Alfonso Cano 
A dactyloscopiste of Cali went to history as the man who confirmed the death of Alfonso Cano'. 
The work of these officials is crucial. 
The past November 4, an ITC dactyloscopiste Cali spent in history as the person who confirmed the identity of the Supreme Leader of the FARC, "Alfonso Cano," contrasting his fingerprints. 
Of the seven dactyloscopistes who work in the local offices of the ITC, this week it was the turn of " Eliazar disponibilité' González, a man of Puerto Tejada, who has worked for 21 years in the field of judicial investigation. 
At the beginning of his career, Gonzalez has worked in the municipes of Chocó, where a lot of times he had to spend more than five days in the forest to get to the place in which the corpses were to be identified. 
The year 2000 was transferred to the capital of Valle and after appropriate courses, he specializes in fingerprinting, which is the study of skin friction, palms and feet. 
During the week of the operation against alias Alfonso Cano had warned Eliazar to take with him clothes at least for three days. 
Something very great expected. 
Friday night he went to Cauca in a helicopter of Palmira. 
He knew that he had to identify two corpses, and that it suspected that one of them was that of the man who headed the oldest guérrilla in the world, therefore asked to carry the card with the ten fingerprints of Guillermo Sáenz León (his real name). 
But when he arrived with the investigative team to the location of the body, it has not recognized by its physical aspect, because it was very different from the one he had seen in the media. 
He had no beard, he was dressed as a peasant in the area, without glasses and much more meagre. 
But fingerprints do not lie. 
Accompanied by a galtonienne microscope, ink, an undertaking the harvest and a lamp, Eliazar compared the fingerprints of the corpse with those of the card. 
His eye did not wrong: it was "Alfonso Cano." 
That same night, the man from Puerto Tejada was the official who confirmed to the Defence Minister, Juan Carlos Pinzón that yes, it was the supreme leader of the FARC. 
In search of the footprint 
For a Sijín dactyloscopiste in Cali recognition that President Juan Manuel Santos Eliazar González, in a press conference for the operation against "Cano," is very significant. 
Many people know our work. 
Fingerprinting is an exact science, with no margin of error, which can be crucial in solving crimes. 
To identify the corpses, the dactyloscopistes supports the investigations for crimes such as theft and homicide and confirm the identity of those captured. 
When caught, many offenders have false identity cards or have no documents. 
We are taking fingerprints and looking in the database. 
The researcher told that in a case of theft he had to remove part of the wall of a house, because in this place the thief had supported his hand to get a safe full of jewelery and money. 
"The walls are difficult because they are not adequate to make a fingerprint, but in this case we were able to obtain the footprint of the hand and identify the offender who had participated in various flights," he says. 
Fingerprints can also dismiss or confirm suspects in cases of homicide. 
Recently we found a man dead, with bottles of drink around him. 
Interlude of the investigation has determined that a parent can be suspect of the crime and an imprint on the bottle. 
Even if this number not guarantee that he is the murderer, this place on the scene of the crime. 
A dactyloscopiste of the ITC explained that extracted "the fingerprints of objects with physical or chemical reagents." 
When they appear, using an undertaking the harvest or a band to collect. 
Subsequently, the prints are sent to Asif, the déclinquents database, or the Civil Registry. 
"The problem is that there is still a lot of undocumented Colombians," said the ITC expert. 
He explained that everything is not how it is shown in the television programme CSI. 
Like all that glitters is not gold, touch is not necessarily a footprint. 
However, it can be used, if it achieves the necessary confrontation. 
